                "summary": "Apple Walnut Brownies requires around <b>1 hour and 15 minutes</b> from start to finish. This dessert has <b>402 calories</b>, <b>7g of protein</b>, and <b>33g of fat</b> per serving. For <b>$1.21 per serving</b>, this recipe <b>covers 12%</b> of your daily requirements of vitamins and minerals. This recipe serves 10. It is an <b>affordable</b> recipe for fans of American food. A mixture of walnut, semi-sweet chocolate, vanillan extract, and a handful of other ingredients are all it takes to make this recipe so flavorful. This recipe is liked by 10 foodies and cooks. It is brought to you by Foodista. Taking all factors into account, this recipe <b>earns a spoonacular score of 37%</b>, which is not so amazing. If you like this recipe, take a look at these similar recipes: <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/walnut-brownies-454785\">Walnut Brownies</a>, <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/walnut-brownies-408645\">Walnut Brownies</a>, and <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/walnut-brownies-408642\">Walnut Brownies</a>.",
